{#

    Page Layout
    -----------

    The main page layout component providing the full HTML structure,
    including header, fonts, Tailwind CSS setup, and common UI components.

    `subtitle`: the page subtitle used in the `<title>` tag and header subtitle.
        Defaults to "Descubra e conecte-se com pesquisadores Lattes".
    `current_page`: the current page number, used to control the GoBackButton visibility.

    Content
    -------
    The main content of the page inserted inside the layout container.

    Usage
    -----

    To create a full page layout with dynamic subtitle and current page:

        <layout.Page subtitle="Pesquisar Pesquisadores" current_page={{2}}>
            ... your page content here ...
        </layout.Page>

#}


